data.description: This beautiful corner lot in Fenwick offers a split floor plan.  The office is spacious with vaulted ceilings and built-ins. The kitchen has beautifully redone cabinets, granite counters, and double ovens. The large living room is open with a gas fireplace and wood look flooring.  The master has a whirlpool tub, walk  in closet and connections for a stackable washer/dryer. The upstairs has a full bath and walk-in closet and could easily be the fifth bedroom or a bonus room. All bedrooms have their own full baths. Laundry room has a sink and great counter and cabinet space. The 3 car garage is extended with a sink and refrigerator space as well as a storm shelter.
